{"id":"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy","title":"ChangeDetectionStrategy","contents":"\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.cn/api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy\", \"name\": \"ChangeDetectionStrategy\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> &gt; <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/change_detection/constants.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\" aria-label=\"提供編輯建議\" title=\"提供編輯建議\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/constants.ts\" aria-label=\"檢視原始碼\" title=\"檢視原始碼\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  \n  <header ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"changedetectionstrategy\">ChangeDetectionStrategy<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#changedetectionstrategy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    \n    <label class=\"api-type-label enum\">enum</label>\n    \n    \n    \n  </header>\n  \n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"short-description\">\n    <p translation-result=\"on\">預設變更檢測器用來檢測更改的策略。設定後，將在下次觸發變更檢測時生效。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">The strategy that the default change detector uses to detect changes.\nWhen set, takes effect the next time change detection is triggered.</p>\n\n\n    \n  </section>\n  \n\n  \n\n  \n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"see-also\">\n  <h2 id=\"see-also\">參見<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#see-also\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <ul>\n  \n    <li><a href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#usage-notes\">Change detection usage</a>\n<a href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#usage-notes\">變更檢測的用法</a>\n</li>\n  </ul>\n</section>\n\n\n  \n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"enum-overview\">\n<code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\">\nenum <a href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy\" class=\"code-anchor\">ChangeDetectionStrategy</a> {\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#OnPush\"><span class=\"member-name\">OnPush</span>: 0</a>\n  <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#Default\"><span class=\"member-name\">Default</span>: 1</a>\n}\n</code-example>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section ng-should-translate=\"\" class=\"members\">\n  <a name=\"properties\"></a>\n  <h2 id=\"members\">成員列表<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#members\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table property-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>成員</th>\n        <th>說明</th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n    \n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"OnPush\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">OnPush</span>: 0</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">使用 <code>CheckOnce</code> 策略，這意味著把此策略設定為 <code>Default</code>（ <code>CheckAlways</code> ）將禁用自動變更檢測，直到重新啟用。變更檢測仍然可以顯式呼叫。此策略適用於所有子指令，並且不能被覆蓋。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the <code>CheckOnce</code> strategy, meaning that automatic change detection is deactivated\nuntil reactivated by setting the strategy to <code>Default</code> (<code>CheckAlways</code>).\nChange detection can still be explicitly invoked.\nThis strategy applies to all child directives and cannot be overridden.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n      <tr class=\"member\">\n        <td>\n          <a id=\"Default\"></a>\n          <code class=\"\"><span class=\"member-name\">Default</span>: 1</code>\n        </td>\n        <td>\n          \n          <div no-translate=\"\"><p translation-result=\"on\">使用預設的 <code>CheckAlways</code> 策略，在該策略中，變更檢測將自動執行，直到顯式停用為止。</p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Use the default <code>CheckAlways</code> strategy, in which change detection is automatic until\nexplicitly deactivated.</p>\n\n</div>\n          \n          </td>\n    </tr>\n    \n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n</section>\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/core\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/global/ComponentDebugMetadata\n - guide/testing-utility-apis\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/core\n - api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#Default\n - api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#OnPush\n - api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#changedetectionstrategy\n - api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#members\n - api/core/ChangeDetectionStrategy#see-also\n - api/core/ChangeDetectorRef#usage-notes\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/edit/aio/packages/core/src/change_detection/constants.ts?message=docs(core)%3A%20請簡述你的修改...\n - https://github.com/angular/angular-cn/tree/12.1.0-next.1/packages/core/src/change_detection/constants.ts\n-->"}